  Tooltips:
  - LanguageKey: English
    Value:
    - Lives near houses and in gardens.
  - LanguageKey: Chinese
    Value:
    - "\u4F4F\u5728\u623F\u5C4B\u9644\u8FD1\u548C\u82B1\u56ED\u91CC\u3002"
  - LanguageKey: French
    Value:
    - "Vit pr\xE8s des maisons et dans les jardins."
  - LanguageKey: Russian
    Value:
    - "\u041E\u0431\u0438\u0442\u0430\u0435\u0442 \u0432\u043E\u0437\u043B\u0435
